Semester Project

Kolin Newby
CSCI4229 Fall 2020

Create detailed scene.

Key bindings
  l          Toggle lighting on/off
  t          Toggle turntable effect
  o          Toggle orbit of moon (resets to original position when off)
  arrows     Change view angle
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  ESC        Exit

To run program:
  - Use "make" command to compile project in the project folder.
  - Run the "main" file with the "./main" command.
  - Use the controls above to minipulate the program.

What to pay to attention to:
  - The detail achieved in the tower and front part of the house, specifically the top of the tower
  - The moon model I made with help from class examples, if you do a full rotation in the default view you will see it
